title: Kyle Wilson (cricketer)
text: Kyle Wilson (born 9 June 1989) is a South African <a href="cricket">cricket</a>er. He played in five <a href="first-class%20cricket">first-class</a> and four <a href="List%20A%20cricket">List A</a> matches for <a href="Border%20%28cricket%20team%29">Border</a> in 2010.
